Nicholas Cosmo Gets 25 Year Term in $413 Million Ponzi Scheme

-- B y   T h o m   W e i d l i c h
-- 
2011-10-14T17:31:20Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-14/nicholas-cosmo-gets-25-year-term-in-413-million-ponzi-scheme.html
Nicholas Cosmo, who pleaded guilty
to running a $413 million Ponzi scheme that defrauded thousands
of investors, was sentenced to 25 years in prison in federal
court in  Central Islip ,  New York , prosecutors said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Thom Weidlich in New York at 
